'''伊塔堡'''是一座历史城堡，位于印度[[阿鲁纳恰尔邦|阿鲁纳恰尔邦]][[伊塔那噶|伊塔那噶]]市[[帕普派尔县|帕普派尔县]]的中心，其年代可追溯到14－15世纪，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://arunachalpradesh.nic.in/tourism.htm |title=Tourism in Arunachal Pradesh |publisher=Arunachalpradesh.nic.in |date= |accessdate=2012-03-27 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120320144930/http://arunachalpradesh.nic.in/tourism.htm |archivedate=2012-03-20 }}</ref>伊塔那噶便是根据它而命名，它是一座形状不规则的城堡，主要用砖建成，砖建筑的总体积为16,200立方米。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.arunachaltourism.com/destination.php |title=Arunachal Tourism |publisher=Arunachal Tourism |date=1911-12-04 |accessdate=2012-03-27 |archive-date=2012-04-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120405211841/http://arunachaltourism.com/destination.php |dead-url=yes }}</ref>其东、西、南三面各有三座大门，据说是由毗邻的[[阿萨姆邦|阿萨姆]]的[[阿豪姆王国|阿豪姆王国]]修建。“伊塔”在[[阿豪姆語|阿豪姆語]]中的字面含义是“砖”。印度考古人员将其在'''伊塔堡'''的考古成果陈立在[[伊塔那噶|伊塔那噶]]市的[[尼赫鲁|尼赫鲁]]博物馆。<ref>{{cite book|title=History, religion and culture of north east India|author=T. Raatan|publisher=Gyan Books|year=2006|isbn=8182051789|page=29|url=http://books.google.co.in/books?id=L8x0ZLkFdFkC&pg=PA29&dq=Jawaharlal+Nehru+Museum,+Itanagar&hl=en&sa=X&ei=fTx9T4GUJ8LirAfbscz4DA&ved=0CF4Q6AEwBw#v=onepage&q=Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20Museum%2C%20Itanagar&f=false|access-date=2014-07-01|archive-date=2014-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714210056/http://books.google.co.in/books?id=L8x0ZLkFdFkC&pg=PA29&dq=Jawaharlal+Nehru+Museum,+Itanagar&hl=en&sa=X&ei=fTx9T4GUJ8LirAfbscz4DA&ved=0CF4Q6AEwBw#v=onepage&q=Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20Museum%2C%20Itanagar&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>

